text: ( Source : NAVSEA - Naval Sea Systems Command ) By PEO LCS Public Affairs | October 19 , 2015 MARINETTE, Wis. -- The U.S. Navy accepted delivery of the future USS Milwaukee (LCS 5) during a ceremony at the Marinette Marine Corporation shipyard
